  "title": "Construction Site Senior Supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Oversee the construction activities and progress, plan, implement and monitor work</li>\n  <li>Schedule in accordance to the master and detailed work programme</li>\n  <li>Liaise with Professional Engineer on the Temporary works</li>\n  <li>Liaise with consultants (QPS) for technical issues and coordinate the site activities with subcontractors</li>\n  <li>Handle of technical and engineering problems</li>\n  <li>Provide guidance to supervisors in relation to construction works, ensure progress according to schedule,</li>\n  <li>Maintain quality standards, carry out site inspections and resolve technical issues on time</li>\n  <li>Prepare report and method statement whenever necessary</li>\n  <li>Manage and control workers and monitor their work closely to keep site safety and neat</li>\n  <li>Supervise ongoing site activities closely</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidates must possess at least a Primary/Secondary/”O” Level, Higher Secondary/College, Professional Certificate/Nitec in any field</li>\n  <li>At least 5 years of working experience in a related field in Timber or Precast Formwork</li>\n</ul>",
